Package: osninterface
Title: Query OpenSky Network State Vectors via DuckDB
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Quentin", "Goens", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lazily query OpenSky Network historical state vector data via DuckDB,
    reading parquet files directly from the OSN S3 bucket. Provides functions
    to fetch daily data and filter by geographic radius around airports using
    DuckDB's spatial extension (Haversine distance).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
